<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='530000' id='t-530000'>It's very safe actually.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='531633' id='t-531633'>And it's fun for the whole family.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 9:08
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='533626' id='t-533626'>(Laughter)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 9:12
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='537984' id='t-537984'>Let's see, I think that's it.
